OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy, but with some
OL,6,Fbrighter or sunny spells. Showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping through the afternoon, most
OL,8,Ffrequent in the west, where they could
OL,9,Fturn heavy with a very isolated rumble
OL,10,Fof thunder. Light winds, and feeling
OL,11,Fwarm in any sunny spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading into the
OL,14,Fevening, with some clear spells
OL,15,Flikely. Low cloud, mist and the odd
OL,16,Fspot of drizzle then spreading inland
OL,17,Ffrom the North Sea. Milder than recent
OL,18,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,167,160,301,260,100,100
