OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain for some, although these
OL,7,Feasing by the afternoon. Cooler than
OL,8,Frecently, especially in the onshore
OL,9,Fbreeze, but turning sunny from the
OL,10,Feast later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FOvernight cloud and mist clearing
OL,14,Fearly Wednesday and Thursday to give
OL,15,Fsome warm sunshine, but tempered by
OL,16,Fstrong onshore breezes. Sunny spells
OL,17,Fand lighter winds Friday, but perhaps
OL,18,Falso showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
